text: State Route 900 (SR 900) is a state highway in the U.S. state of Washington in King County. The highway's west end is at Interstate 5 (I-5) in Tukwila. Its east end is at I-90 in Issaquah. SR 900 also meets I-405 in Renton. The highway is long. ==References== Category:Roads in Washington (state)
title: Washington State Route 900
